====== Arrows ======

[[http://www.haskell.org/arrows/]]

An abstraction of computations, more general than monads.

[[GHC]] provides [[http://www.haskell.org/ghc/docs/7.2.1/html/users_guide/arrow-notation.html|support for the notation]] described in the link above, it can be turned on using ''-XArrows'' command-line flag.

